Details


ITEM#: 17261641

Relish the outdoors with a set just as unique as your outdoor patio with the Nelson bistro set. This set offers a solid foundation of metal and resin wicker. Creates a look that is not only trendy but functional. Whether you are entertaining guests or simply enjoying the outdoors the Nelson bistro set will satisfy for years to come.

Includes: Two (2) chairs and one (1) table 
Materials: Metal and resin wicker
Color: Multi-brown
Assembly required: Yes
Chair dimensions: 34.75 inches high x 25 inches wide x 25.50 inches deep 
Chair seat dimensions: 19.50 inches high x 16 inches wide x 20.50 inches deep
Chair weight: 13-pounds
Table dimensions: 28.50 inches high x 26 inches wide x 26 inches deep
Table weight: 16-pounds
Material: Metal, WickerStyle: CasualAssembly: Assembly RequiredColor: Brown





