Details


ITEM#: 16649057

The Nelson bench with cushion makes a great transitional piece for
your home. With its natural dark tones and attention to detail
shown in the cushion and ties on the seat this bench will complete
any room you place it into. Enjoy this cushioned bench ottoman for
years to come. Sturdy acacia wood construction makes this bench from
Christopher Knight Home a long-lasting addition to your home. Place
it in your entryway to provide family and guests with a comfortable
place to put on and remove their shoes, or use it at the foot of
your bed as a handy place to set clothing or other items as you get
ready to sleep. Includes: One (1) bench with cushions Materials: Acacia wood Upholstery material: Polyester blend fabric Color: Rich mahogany Upholstery color: Ivory cushion Finish: Mahogany Assembly required: Yes Dimensions: 19.75 inches high x 47.25 inches wide x 17.75
  inches deep Weight: 15.43-pounds





